author: Google
description: Ever struggled to understand a complex concept? We’re introducing a game-changer with Gemini 3 in Search that uses a coding agent to build bespoke, interactive simulations and tools on the fly. We brought together some of our team to give you a behind-the-scenes look. #GoogleSearch #Gemini3
title: Behind the scenes of how Gemini 3 in Search can code Interactive simulations for you

author: Google
description:
Get into the spirit this season with festive – though not entirely real – Christmas comedies that show how Google Search can help save your holiday. #JustAskGoogle #AIMode

Not coming to a theater near you! (In partnership with NBCUniversal)

When chronic bad-gifter Jack Coal finds himself on the Naughty List and out of his girlfriend’s life, he’ll have to search for the perfect present to win her back by Christmas. With the help of AI Mode in Google Search and Santa’s “Chief Executive Elf” Joy, he might just find his way back on the Nice List. 

Starring: Nicolas Vansteenberghe, Ciara Miller and Nicole Byer
